Sardar Azmoun admits he would be open to a move to Liverpool. #lfc (Echo)<br />
<br />
Azmoun: &ldquo;I have no received any offers. If there are, I&rsquo;m going to take my time to look, whether it&rsquo;s come from Liverpool or other clubs.&rdquo;

Lovren on his partnership with Matip:<br />
<br />
&quot;It&rsquo;s always easier when you have the feeling with your partner and know each other. To be honest we&rsquo;ve done it quite well, even in pre-season, it was really quick &ndash; I don&rsquo;t know why, maybe because he&rsquo;s speaking German and I&rsquo;m speaking German, maybe that&rsquo;s the funny thing.&quot;

